ygData.messageBody:
The first named NPC Qeynos newbies run into. He's a named gnoll only level
4 or 5 but he puts the fear of gnoll into all the 2's and 3's in North
Qeynos. He does a lot of shouting and someone should petition the GM's to
have him tone it down <g> (not as bad that that guy in the commons who wants
to duel Altunic though.)

Snyak
